&lt;p&gt;N2CMS runs just fine on any ASP.NET based host, and I would encourage you to find the web hosting solution that best meets your needs. A great free option which works particularly well as a &amp;ldquo;backup&amp;rdquo; hosting plan or for development use is Windows Azure Websites, which you can access at www.windowsazure.com.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;As a fallback, I can offer a limited number of people $15/month web hosting, which allows you unlimited domain names, one IIS site root on a platform that supports .NET 4.5., 5 GB of disk space, and &amp;ldquo;unlimited&amp;rdquo; bandwidth (for most normal uses). The $15/month cost helps defray the cost of maintaining the servers and also helps support further development on N2CMS. There is no &amp;quot;extra&amp;quot; tech support included, and I don&amp;#39;t offer this service to make a profit.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;How to get web hosting: Contact me at ben@herila.net if you are interested in the $15/month option.&lt;/p&gt;

